@baseUrl = http://localhost:3002
@json = application/json

### Happy path: create session
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "programId": "yoga_basics",
  "startTime": "2025-09-01T10:00:00Z",
  "durationMinutes": 60,
  "maxCapacity": 10,
  "coachName": "Coach A"
}

### List sessions for program
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions?programId=yoga_basics

### Debug: list recorded domain events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/_debug/events

### Create pilates session
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "programId": "pilates_intro",
  "startTime": "2025-09-02T12:00:00Z",
  "durationMinutes": 45,
  "maxCapacity": 12
}
